x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Fender-Sam@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Fender-Sam@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Fender-Sam@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827863" class="wp-caption-text">山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）现场表演。信用：迪迪埃·梅斯斯/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>He <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-plays-live-debut-for-two-unreleased-songs-people-watching-and-nostalgia-lies-3780786">first debuted &#39;People Watching&#39; live, along with another unreleased song, &#39;Nostalgia&#39;s Lie&#39;</a> in August, with both set to appear on the tracklist. Following the title track being shared, Fender <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-details-of-new-album-people-watching-3812366">revealed details surrounding the record</a> , including its tracklisting. It was produced by Fender alongside his bandmates Dean Thompson, Joe Atkinson, producer Markus Dravs, and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-War-on-Drugs">The War on Drugs</a> &#39; Adam Granduciel.</p><p> In other Sam Fender news, the singer was announced as <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announced-as-record-store-day-uk-official-ambassador-3834386">the official ambassador of</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announced-as-record-store-day-uk-official-ambassador-3834386">Record Store Day UK</a> 2025 – set for April 12 – and will release two new songs as part of a special EP to celebrate.</p><p> He <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">is also nominated for two BRIT Awards</a> at next month&#39;s ceremony: Artist Of The Year and Alt/Rock Act.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-more-huge-uk-outdoor-shows-for-summer-2025-3837652">Sam Fender announces more huge UK outdoor